<p>Updates to The Ship have been released. The updates will be applied automatically when your Steam client is restarted. The specific changes include:<br/><br/><b>The Ship</b><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Fixed crash when changing key bindings</li></ul></p>
